title: EP.53: DOLPHINS SHOW OUT, STEELERS WANT PICKETT, TREY LANCE INJURY, PACKERS VS BUCS, AND MUCH MORE!
description: Tune in and get all the action from week one! From the Dolphins comeback to the Steelers struggles. Get our predictions for next weeks big games like the Packers vs Buccaneers. We transcend just an NFL podcast because we get into many sports but you can never have enough NFL talk. Tune in now!
